title: Cerebus Companion 1-2 with questions
description:
Issues 1-2 of 'Cerebus Companion'

Win-Mill Productions, 1993-1994, 44 pages each

Produced by Craig Miller

With assistance from John Thorne

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

OK, truthfully, after all these years, I don't find these books nearly as interesting as I did at the time of their release. They're cool as time capsules and as an item for completists to fill out their collections. But beyond that, after all these years of online information sharing and discussion, they don't hold a lot of value in relation to the series. So, what I REALLY want to know is...

Cerebus Archive 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 8, 9, 10 out of 11 - missing 6, 7, 11
Following Cerebus 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 10, 11 out of 12 - missing 9, 12

That's what I have, that's what I'm missing.

Do y'all want me to upload them?

Does anybody have the missing issues?

Maybe together we can organize and upload complete runs on these.
